{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-438-integer-part-of-polynomial-equations-solutions","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 438: Deo celog broja rešenja polinomske jednačine","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za tupu celobrojnih brojeva $t = (a_1, \\ldots, a_n)$, neka je $(x_1, \\ldots, x_n)$ rešenje polinomske jednačine $x^n + a_1x^{n - 1} + a_2x^{n - 2} + \\ldots + a_{n - 1}x + a_n = 0$.</p>\n<p>Obratite pažnju na sledeća dva uslova:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$x_1, \\ldots, x_n$ sve su realni.</li>\n<li>Ako su $x_1, \\ldots, x_n$ postavljeni, $⌊x_i⌋ = i$ za $1 ≤ i ≤ n$. ($\\lfloor\\cdot\\rfloor$: funkcija za pod.)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>U slučaju $n = 4$, postoji 12 tupela za cele brojeve koji zadovoljavaju oba uslova.</p>\n<p>Definišemo $S(t)$ kao zbir vrednosti celih brojeva u $t$.</p>\n<p>Za $n = 4$ možemo dokazati da $\\sum S(t) = 2087$ za sve tuple $t$ koje zadovoljavaju oba uslova.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $\\sum S(t)$ za $n = 7$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5231000cf542c510034","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302109,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-438-integer-part-of-polynomial-equations-solutions"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function polynomialIntegerPart() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npolynomialIntegerPart();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>polynomialIntegerPart()</code> treba vratiti <code>2046409616809</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(polynomialIntege